name: Battlestation: Harbinger
description: Battlestation: Harbinger is a science fiction space exploration game from Bugbyte Ltd.

name: Halcyon Sun: Episodes 1 & 2
description: Halcyon Sun is an episodic space combat game, originally released for free via download. Framed as an interactive sci-fi show, it featured heavily scripted gameplay and cutscenes.

name: Dukes of Hazzard
description: Dukes of Hazzard is a driving game with an overhead perspective, based on the popular television series of the same name. Players take on the role of the Duke boys driving the infamous "General Lee," while trying to avoid the police and rescue their sister Daisy from Boss Hogg. While development of this game was reportedly complete, it was not commercially released (and thus it never recieved a packaging design, official instruction manual, etc).

name: Ratpad vs Everglide: Battle of the Pads
Crazy Factory
description: Crazy Factory VR is a bunch of silly virtual reality mini-games in an automated robotic factory. You are a robot working in a factory directed by an artificial intelligence. Carve shoes, punch pickaxes, throw crystal glasses and uncover the truth !

name: Aloadae
description:
The Game:

Aloadae is a Open World Horror Game based on Cryengine V. Developed by a small team called Bleeding Colors . The game is set in the pacific northwest in Washington state. A thick fog will cover the game world during the whole experience. The view distance is very restricted to give the player the feeling of being isolated in a mysterious environment.

Core Features:

• Open world landscape which invites for exploring
• Intense horror gameplay
• Explore mysterious places which are so scary that you just exit the game
• Beautiful dynamic weather and day/night cycle
• Non-linear game play

name: Blossom & Decay
description: Blossom & Decay is a browser-based, sandbox MMO ARPG that is set at the edge of a dying realm. It brings action combat together with crafting and survival mechanics, in an open world where players are able to develop their unique story experience.

name: Defense Keeper
description: Sci Fi tower defense where you can save ur progress cross platform

name: Metro 2033 Wars: Born in the Dark
Lost Within
description:
A city in ruins, hell on earth: Seph Garrett is a police officer running away from certain death. He will find himself trapped inside lost within his own city...alone, wounded. Searching for help he will find someone else alive: they are close and distant at the same time, but they will need to work togheter to survive.

Lost Within is a RPG/Survival Horror/Stealth hybrid made with RPG Maker VX, coming soon on PC.

name: Lost Coffee
description: A coffee shop simulator that's not a simulator game. Something strange is going on in this shop.

name: Reset
description: Reset is a single player co-op first person puzzle game with a strong emphasis on story and atmosphere. The unique game mechanic in Reset is the ability to travel back in time to solve puzzles co-operatively, with yourself.

name: Legacy
description:
Legacy is a Third Person Shooter-Adventure and Puzzle solving Game made by one person.

The story of the game is still in progress and it will be revealed and updated in future posts. For now I can say that the action will be an episodic one, almost each episode will contain some scenery, landscape, monument or location from the real word and also some historical accuracy. Some facts or places might be altered to support the game's flow and story.

The player must travel, explore and solve puzzles in order to accomplish his Legacy.

name: Zhombre, the Undead Hombre
description: Zhombre, The Undead Hombre is an Action Platformer set in a post apocalyptic world 100 years after the zombie invasion. Humans are the apex predator and the Undead have been forced to find refuge on the outskirts of human encampments. Zhombre wields his brothers severed leg in his fight against the human scourge. Follow him from The Barren Wastelands into the Neon city of the Living in his quest for vengeance as he uncovers the truth of the past.

name: Strawberry Shortcake: And Her Berry Best Friends
description: An endless runner starring Strawberry Shortcake.

name: SuperCollapse! II
description: The first in the Collapse! series to be released in retail.

name: Baseball Mogul 2006
description: The 2006 version of this PC only career baseball management simulation.

name: Madden NFL 07: Hall of Fame Edition
Shaun White Snowboarding: Target Edition
description: The special Target edition of the game has exclusive extended content and features that consumers won't be able to find anywhere else, including the Target Mountain – an entire mountain environment found only in the Target edition. Gamers will also be able to take advantage of exclusive jibs and additional scenes. Additionally, players will be able to cozy up in the game's virtual version of the Target Chalet, the real-life mountainside home where Shaun and his fellow Target athletes hang out with friends and family at the annual Winter X Games in Aspen, Colorado. Among other exclusive features, the Target Chalet is the only indoor environment anywhere in the game.

name: Finding Nemo: Learning with Nemo
description: Fun for young children with Nemo, learning patterns, shapes and comparison skills.

name: FOX Sports Racing
description: A soccer game by Gremlin Interactive.

name: PlanetSide: Core Combat
description: Core Combat is the one and only expansion for the first-person shooter MMO Planetside.

name: Combat Mission II: Barbarossa to Berlin
description: Combat Mission II: Barbarossa to Berlin is a turn-based computer game about tactical battles in World War II. It is part of the Combat Mission series. The game has been described as the "reigning champ of east front tactical warfare for the PC." [1]

name: World War I: The Great War
Finding Nemo: Escape to the Big Blue - Special Edition
Vampire Moon: The Mystery of the Hidden Sun
Mabinogi Duel
description: A mobile TCG that is available for iOS and Android.

name: Star Trek: Alien Domain
description: Star Trek: Alien Domain is a free to play browser game by GameSamba and CBS Interactive in which the player has to establish a base, upgrade their starship and conquer territories.

name: Tribal Wars 2
description: Tribal Wars 2 is the sequel to the classic Tribal Wars. Starting out with a small village, one of your goals is to build it up into a strong castle, fortified by impregnable city walls. But Tribal Wars 2 is much more than just a simple strategy city building game - you also have to assemble an army by recruiting and training soldiers, such as axemen or spear fighters. With them, you are able to defend and expand your kingdom in the free-to-play medieval strategy game.

name: Dawn of the Dragons
description: Dawn of the Dragons is a MMO RPG application developed by 5th Planet Games that utilizes the free-to-play business model, wherein the essential game play is free, while special options and items become available with the purchase and use of a currency known as Planet Coins with real-world money.

name: Legend Online
description: Legend Online is an MMO game.

name: Rise of Mythos
description: Rise of Mythos is a MMORPG trading card game.

name: Rail Nation
description: Construct your rail empire within a browser and, together with other players, develop the right strategy to become the most influential tycoon of all time.

name: SD Gundam Online
description: The latest entry in the longrunning series of Gundam strategy RPG's, SD Gundam G Generation Genesis is being developed to launch on PlayStation 3, PlayStation 4 and PlayStation Vita in 2016 as part of Gundam's 30th Anniversary

name: Archlord 2
description: A free-to-play MMORPG with hybrid classes and guild warfare.

name: League of Angels
description: In a time of darkness, new heroes must rise to re-awaken fallen Angels and save the world. League of Angels is a hybrid MMORPG developed by GTArcade and co-published by R2Games.

name: SpongeBob SquarePants Bowling
description: SpongeBob SquarePants Bowling is a mobile game developed by Backbone Entertainment and published by THQ Wireless for Brew and Java.

name: Dragon Pals
description: Dragon Pals is a side-scrolling, browser-based MMORPG published by R2Games.

name: Hello Hero
description: Hello Hero is a free-to-play role-playing game from Fincon.

name: Ancient Ruins 1: The Crypt of the King
Pirate Storm
description: Blast modern day pirates in this shooter. Available on iPhone, iPad, and Droid devices this summer.

name: Kasparov Chessmate
description: A chess game co-designed by chess grandmaster Garry Kasparov. Players can face off against the computer or with other players in local multiplayer.

name: 4evolve: Deep Stars
description: 4evolve: Deep Stars is a space sim 4X game set in randomly generated galaxy. DEEP STARS is extraordinary space game beyond the typical simulator. You take the role of spaceship Nomad, for which the player creates a career path. You can grow as a trader, smuggler or captain of the fleet. Buy and sell various goods. Create and develop your space empire! The game is open-ended, and you are free shape your career. You can sign and break alliances with the various races fighting for power, freedom and oxygen sources!

name: Hitman Go: VR Edition
description:
Experience Hitman Go, a turn-based strategy game with beautifully rendered diorama-style set pieces in VR.

You will strategically navigate fixed spaces on a grid to avoid enemies and take out your target or infiltrate well-guarded locations. You really have to think about each move and all the Hitman tools of the trade you would expect are included; disguises, distractions, sniper rifles and even 47’s iconic Silverballers.

name: Supipara
description: An episodic visual novel developed by Minori.

name: K-1 World Grand Prix 2001
description: K-1 World Grand Prix 2001 is a Kickboxing game, developed by KCEJ and published by Konami, which was released in Japan in 2001.

name: Golf Resort Tycoon II
description: Golf Resort Tycoon II is a simulation game in which the player is tasked with creating a successful golf course.

name: Out of the Park Baseball 4
description: The fourth installment in the baseball simulation franchise.

name: Mimesis Online
description: Mimesis Online is an online role-playing game which was developed and published by Tannhauser Gate

name: Harukoi Otome: Greetings from the Maidens' Garden
Word Soup
description: Word Soup is an XNA community game available over Xbox Live Marketplace. It is a word game where the aim is to make words from connecting blocks.

name: Extraction: Project Outbreak
description: A top down military themed shooter.

name: Bugs Wars
description: Rugrats in Paris follows the Rugrats on their big adventure to France. Play as Tommy, Chuckie, and even Reptar as you make new adventures.

name: Star Fox Zero: Limited First Print Edition
Star Wars: The Battle for Hoth
description: Star Wars: The Battle for Hoth is a tower defense game based on the opening battle of The Empire Strikes Back. Place units and structures strategically to stop Imperial forces in 15 levels. Upgrade units and unlock Fortress mode for limited resources.

name: AerialDrop
description: A HTML5 Turn Based Mech Shooter. Competitive and seasonal gameplay!

name: PlayStation Move
description: An app that lets one play supported PlayStation Home games on the Vita.

name: Blades of Fury
description: 3D arcade fighting game for the iPhone and iPod Touch, and the spiritual successor to "Age of Glory: Medieval Combat", a mobile phone game

name: Starfall Tactics
description: Starfall Tactics is a hardcore mix of RTS and Wargame genres powered by Unreal Engine 4, which allows you to build a space fleet of your dreams, battle against other players in quick and ranked matches and discover a huge Galaxy you can conquer. Exciting quick PvP matches for advanced strategists and wargamers, challenging PvE missions, plenty of tactical choices, in-depth customization of every unit in your army, nice visual component and a huge open world for MMO fans - it's all about this game.

name: Glory Quest
description:
Glory Quest is a 2d top-down hack and slash RPG

Features:
Large map to explore
6 types of creatures to hunt down and kill
Battle System

name: Morning Men
description: Take a trip back to the golden age of science fiction as Morning Men blends an out-of-this-world story with point-and-click adventuring and turn-based JRPG-style combat. Each character has his or her own traits, which can be changed based on your decisions made throughout your adventure. Help, hurt, or even ruin one of your companions lives by either masterfully or carelessly picking your next narrative step.

name: The Secrets of Da Vinci: The Forbidden Manuscript
Superbikes Riding Challenge
description: A motorcycle racing game released on the PC and PS2 exclusively in PAL regions.

name: Maelstrom
description: Maelstrom is an Asteroids clone created in 1992 by Ambrosia Software.

name: Kudos: Rock Legend
description: Kudos: Rock Legend is a fantastic turn based RPG about living the life of a rock star.

name: First Eagles: The Great Air War 1918
The Fast and the Furious: Tokyo Drift
Crane Simulator 2009
description: The most realistic crane simulator experience since the critically acclaimed Crane Simulator 2008, Crane Simulator 2009 adds such exciting new features as physics and a moveable crane arm.

name: Chocobo Racing 3D
description: Chocobo Racing 3D was the codename of a Chocobo game being developed for the Nintendo 3DS. The game was announced at E3 2010, although it was unknown whether it was going to be an original game or a remake of the first Chocobo Racing game (whose full title was actually Chocobo Racing ~Genkai e no Rōdo~ in Japan). On October 10th, 2013, Takashi Tokita said that the game is canceled.

name: Chocobo de Mobile
description: Chocobo de Mobile is a Miscellaneous game, developed and published by Square Enix, which was released in Japan in 2006.

name: Dokodemo Chocobo 3: Taose! Niji Iro Daimaou
Fighter Squadron: The Screamin' Demons Over Europe
Left 4 Dead: The Survival Pack
description:
First off, you can now play the two campaigns Death Toll and Dead Air online in Versus mode. These maps have been tweaked slightly to remove some closets and to balance gameplay. For example, downstairs in the Boathouse Finale has been significantly emptied to prevent corner camping, and more walls break open.

The anticipated Survival Mode is released, which pits The Survivors against endless waves of the horde, as well as multiple Special Infected. Players can hold out in 16 maps, 15 of which are extracts from Crescendo Events and finales from the four original campaigns. These maps have also been tweaked to remove exploits and to make the whole experience much harder. The last map is in the new campaign: The Last Stand, and currently has one map: The Lighthouse.

name: Candy Train
description: New iPhone/iPad game from PopCap. Collect candy and keep your train from crashing.

name: Sir Benfro's Brilliant Balloon
description:
Fly Sir Benfro through beautiful new lands. Float into forests, across oceans and down into the centre of the Earth. But take care! You’re never far from bumping into the next bizarre beast.
Magical fireflies power Sir Benfro’s balloon. Fly as fast as you can to keep collecting the fireflies and reach the end of each adventure.

name: Incoboto
description: A smart little mobile puzzle game

name: Luftwaffe Commander
description: Luftwaffe Commander is a World War II flight sim. It was part of SSI's Living Battlefield series.

name: North vs. South: The Great American Civil War
description: A strategic recreation of the civil war using a game engine designed to recreate ancient warfare in the "Great Battles" series

name: Project Awakening
description: "It's time for the wolves of war to awaken..."

name: Bunker
description:
"Deeply social massive multiplayer alternate history RPG in the post-apocalyptic Soviet Union world with permadeath and open market"

Google Translation and small edit:
"An indie game which is set in a post-apocalyptic world of the future. With a Fallout ideological style world. What self-respecting game developer does not try to make your fallout with shelters and perks?"

name: Save the Whales
description:
Originally to be released in 1983 by 20th Century Fox, this game was not released during the Atari 2600's lifetime. "Save The Whales" is a game in which the player, as a submarine, must protect whales by stopping nets, harpoons, and radioactive waste.

The game was one of three whichs sales were to raise funds for environmental groups. The other two "Dutch Elm Defender" and "Attack of the Baby Seals" were never programmed.

"Save the Whales" was thought to be lost until it was rediscovered in 2002 and thereafter sold at the 2002 Classic Gaming Expo.

name: Struckd
description: The free game creation app for iOS and Android

name: Deadwood: The Forgotten Curse
description:
Deadwood: The Forgotten Curse is an action/adventure game with a unique survival twist. You play as Lathe, a teenage woodling and an avid inventor. During your adventure you are accompanied by a stone giant named Roguard and together you must fight back a horde of wooden zombies, better known as “The Deadwood”, and stop their curse from spreading through the land of Knottington.

By day, Roguard will protect you from the Deadwood allowing you the freedom to explore the land of Knottington. You’ll scavenge for resources and then use those resources to craft your weapons and defenses because when the sun sets, Roguard falls fast asleep leaving you alone to fight back the Deadwood and protect your stone companion. With the right balance of strategy and skill you may just survive the night.

name: Auditorium Duet
description: Auditorium Duet, from CipherPrime, is the upcoming sequel to the PC/PS3 game Auditorium, a music-focused puzzle game. Funded through Kickstarter, Auditorium Duet will release eventually for PC/Mac, prominently featuring co-operative play.

name: Battlesloths
description:
Battlesloths is the fast-paced local multiplayer competitive twin-stick shooter of your slothy dreams. Compete with up to 4 human players or play against AI sloths should you be short of friends. Use a myriad of weaponry, each with their own strategies, to destroy your enemies in a quest to collect the most pizza.

With 12 unique weapons, 7 game modes, customizable battle settings, team vs. options, free for all, a nuke and more hats than you can fit on 50 sloths heads; you’ll have plenty to do as you train to become the ultimate gun-toting, hoverboarding, pizza eating sloth on the block! Revel in the silliness of the slothpacalypse, shoot everything that moves and start hoarding pizza!

name: Off the Leash
description:
There’s a new Chief of Police in town, and he’s put a ban on dogs, ordering them all to be captured! It’s your task to outrun those pesky cops and evade capture, whilst trying to rescue as many of your doggy pals as you can. Along the way you’ll need to eat food, collect coins, complete missions, and do all you can to avoid capture!
You’ll begin playing as a Golden Retriever, collecting coins as you go which can later be spent on various items in the store. Unlock new dogs, collect custom clothing, unleash super power-ups, and call on the mysterious Big Dog for help!

name: Caverns of Minos
description: Caverns of Minos is a freaky twist on Caverns of Mars by Llamasoft, the home of freaky twists on 8-bit video games.

name: Tricky Truck
description: Parkour a truck through a level and park it at the end. It has online high scores and replays.

name: Surgery Simulator
description: A simulation game where you take on the role of a surgeon working in a busy hospital. It should be noted this game is for entertainment purposes only, and unfortunately will not train you to become a surgeon.

name: Red Turn: The Road to Berlin 1943-45
X-Plane
description:
A flight simulator having global simulation capability. Special mission assignments can be used to test skills.
Planes range from regular airlines , fighter aircraft, trainers, historical airplanes, prototypes, and fictional ones.

name: Garbage Truck Simulator 2011
description: Garbage Truck! is a simplistic game designed for very young children.

name: Mythos
description: Mythos is an online, action role-playing game that is free to download and free to play. Set in the land of Uld - a fantasy world arising from the ashes of an epoch-long war of darkness - players assume the roles of fantasy heroes as they explore, adventure, and quest through entirely randomized dungeons and environments. With an elegant point-and-click interface and an accessible "isometric" perspective, Mythos is poised to have near-universal appeal.

name: Battleground 2: Gettysburg
description: Battleground is a series of turn-based strategy video games developed and published by TalonSoft for Microsoft Windows between 1995 and 1999. Nine games were released in the series, each based on a different historical battle.

name: LMA Manager 2001
description: LMA Manager 2001 is the second game in the LMA Manager series. It was released in March 2001.

name: Konami 80's Arcade Gallery
description: A compilation of six Data East games for Commodore 64.

name: Pool Tour Master
description:
Greetings Troopers, 
If you are a lover of snooker & pool games, you have to play Pool Tour Masters. A billiards game where you can experience pool and snooker like never before, with a big and strong online tours to challenge your friends around the world. Achieve big rewards playing 1 vs 1 tour mode, and get new cues with powerful skills and effects. You have to find your personal cue between more than 60 different cues. Play one of the 3 main modes, against other players in the world, in exciting themed localizations like Sydney, Jamaica, Moscow… Pool Tour Masters is available for Windows Phone 8.1 and Windows 10 mobile.
Game Features
- Touch to aim and hit the ball
- Play with friends and users all over the world in 3 amazing modes
- Over 60 cues to collect
- Log in every day to get big rewards



Download:
http://bit.ly/2aw6YrX

Video & Images:  
https://youtu.be/hSwpDA_x8Wg
https://www.dropbox.com/sh/cgra2i8gcyereqx/AAD5e7hHDJiJ4gAQCaoYJXqwa?dl=0
We will appreciate any coverage of this release in your media.

name: Icebox
description:
The Icebox is a Speedrunning FPS set inside a virtual labyrinth. Use glitch and jet boosts to navigate increasingly challenging environments and sentinels on a mission to search and destroy the Central AI.

Choose how you play the game:

SPEEDRUN MODE

Race the clock, manage resources, and destroy the sentinels on your way through ever more challenging environments culminating in the final battle against the Central AI. Levels are around 2-5min in length. Completing each level inside the Par Time unlocks the next and posts your score on the Leaderboard. Replay levels to perfect your run and improve your overall score.

CAMPAIGN MODE

Take a more considered approach through one giant procedural level, saving as often as you like, with no loading screens, on a solitary journey to search and destroy the Central AI. Commencing with a brief tutorial, the campaign walks you through the game’s mechanics before launching you into progressively harder environments and sentinel battles on your way to the Central AI.

FEATURES

Two Game Modes - Unlockable Speedruns & Single-Player Campaign
Use Glitch - Slow time, bypass gravity, engage shield & boost telekinesis
Use Jet Jumps - Navigate the environment using multi-jumps
Fight AI Squads - Old school FPS with a few extra twists
Hack Terminals - Use terminals to access the network
Use Network Gun - Remotely activate network items
Find Secret Panels - Search for hidden panels and loot
Randomised Worlds - Every play through is unique
Top the Leaderboards - Perfect your run and earn the top spot
Enjoy Dynamic Music - Reacts to your inputs
Make Custom Levels - Design & share your own creations

name: Epic Fly
description:
Welcome to a magical world. A beautiful and peaceful world. Get out of stress. Just play and relax.

Instructions:
Help the toy plane to get home.
Tap the screen to fly through the forest. 
Avoid obstacles from your path. 
Collect the points to achieve high score.
Succes.

Description:
Beautiful landscapes. Relaxing sounds. Nature and forests. Amazing graphics. Nice story.
Nature lover? Or you want to escape from crowded city? This is the way. The best relaxing game.

name: I'm Joshua
description:
- “The United States of America from the 19th Century”, is portrayed in evocative graphics which is displayed in pixel art.
- An original story with an engaging and addictive narrated adventure, which is composed of 3 chapters. Experience the opportunity to fight for your freedom and that of your people!
- There are dozens of characters to communicate with; will you manage to figure out who really wants help? Remember that trusting the wrong person may be fatal!
- There are many cut scenes where you will really have to engage at a rapid rate. Timing is everything, and quite often you will need to make some truly tough decisions.
- English is the capital language spoken throughout the game; however subtitles are available in different languages.

name: Chickens Can't Fly
description: Chickens can't fly, but they sure can fall into a series of wacky traps and powerups!

name: Allied Star Police
description: Conceived by a 10-year-old kid through the Make a Wish Foundation, this game was developed by the people at Popcap Games.

name: Dragon Fantasy
description: Dragon Fantasy (also known as Dragon Fantasy Book 1 ) is a 8-bit JRPG styled game for the iOS and PlayStation platforms.

name: Blast Ball
description: A fun cartoon-like football scramble game

name: Magnetic Billiards: Blueprint
description: Magnetic Billiards: Blueprint is a iOS title which involves clever manipulation of virtual spheres. Points are awarded for creative ball bouncing.

name: Human Defense
description: The earth was invaded by aliens, and human beings resisted alien species and deduced the most meticulous battle outcome with the simplest control method

name: Slydris
description:
Quick thinking and nimble fingers are required to do well.
Slydris is a highly polished and customizable puzzle game for all ages. Select from 3 music tracks and dark or light backgrounds.

name: Scotland Yard: The Hunt for Mr X
World Rally Championship 3
description: The last main installment of SNK's arcade soccer series adds a variety of new features (including a new game mode) while increasing the total team count to 80 playable teams.

name: Heroes Call
description: A free to play Action RPG dungeon crawler for the iOS and Android.

name: Reiner Knizia's Samurai
description: A turn-based strategy game set during feudal Japan. You goal is to gain the most influence from the 3 major castes.

name: Star Wars Pinball: The Empire Strikes Back
Fluxx
description:
Playdek and Looney Labs team up to bring this amazingly fun card game to mobile devices. Fluxx fuses its chaotic and fun game play with offline and online features that fans have come to love in Playdek games!
Featuring New Rule cards that change the rules of the game and Action cards that create chaos. Even the object of winning the game changes during play, as players swap out one Goal card for another.

name: Ollo
description: An educational game for young children featuring a ball of clay called Ollo.

name: Super Ox Wars
description: Super Ox Wars is a polarity-style scrolling shooter from Llamasoft.

name: Dropchord
description: Dropchord is an arcade-style music game from Double Fine playable with the Leap Motion Controller for PC and Mac. The iOS version is soon to follow.

name: Altus 24
description: Altus 24 is a game about an angel participating in a ceremonial ritual that involves ascending several giant towers, conquering the bosses on each of their roofs. The game cycles continuously between three "phases": Build, Spawn, and Action. In the build phase, you have access to an inventory of building items which you can use to construct platforms and mechanisms to help you scale further up the tower. After each build phase, new enemies spawn into the tower. Finally, in the action phase, the game unfreezes itself, and you are given 15 seconds to achieve as much as you can. This includes climbing higher, fighting enemies, and opening treasure chests. The latter two provide you with cards, which can be flipped over during the build phase, awarding you with random building blocks, potions, new weapons, upgrades, and other helpful items.

name: Professional Farmer 2017: Gold Edition
description:
Get ready for the rural lifestyle! This game is set on your own farm! Enjoy the life of a farmer with all its amazing tasks and challenges! Drive your original vehicles, cultivate your fields, take care of your animals and market your produce! Different seasons and weather conditions guarantee realistic game fun. 
 
Earn from your experiences as a farmer, use your knowledge to enjoy the satisfaction a farmer feels when sitting in front of the fireplace in a beautiful farmhouse after a hard working day. Your efforts will be rewarded – the better your fields are tilled, the more animals you breed, the more products you produce, the better the income available for new machines, larger fields and tractors. Get ready for the ultimate farming fun!

name: Soldier of Steel
description: The Man of Steel and the citizen-soldiers of our nation’s militia join forces to protect the peace and prosperity of average citizens in a multi-faceted electronic romp that spans an array of electronic gadgets that would be at home on any utility belt.

name: The Adventures of Victor and Garu
Where Angels Cry: Hell Broke Loose
Trex and Muscle Sam: A New Kickstart!
description:
The two protagonists, Trex and Muscle Sam, are the sons of two legends of the tag team wrestling working in the same company where their fathers had a fundamental role in its creation. Unlike their fathers, Trex and Sam are not very successful on the ring and don't have many fans.

Trex is an egocentric maniac that tries desperately to achieve success, but is actually an insecure nerd on the inside. He's Muscle Sam childhood friend and he's one of the few people that can understand what he says.

Muscle Sam most distinctive tract is that he's an anthropomorphic cat, but it's not a weird occurrence in a world where everyone impersonates their gimmick. He's not a very talkative guy, mostly because very few people can understand what he says. What Sam thinks is a mystery: sometimes he acts like a very brilliant person, sometimes like an instinctive animal.

name: La chute des tours
description: Suitable for all ages, "La chute des tours" is an asymmetric game where every piece is unique and can become the masterpiece of your strategy. From the beginning of the game play, you will have the opportunity to place your towers and to startle your opponent. But be careful, the opposite is possible too ! Developed in order to drastically reduce predictable situations for those who have an advanced level, the game also offer multiple combinations, thanks to which beginners can also get by. Even though the learning of the properties of all pieces will seem complex and tricky in the beginning, the richness of available movments will allow you a gret freedom of action. And always keep in mind that if chance could bring you opportunities, only the one who has taken the right decisions at the right time will have the upper hand. Now, your turn to play !

name: Indiana Jones and the Fate of Atlantis: Special Edition
description:
As of March 2017, the development of the fan remake came to a halt as Disney and LucasFilm games stated they didn't want to share the Indy license at the moment.

“We have been told that Lucasfilm don’t want to share the Indy license with anyone right one,” the team’s Facebook page reads. “We will keep in touch with Lucasfilm people and continuously trying to obtain a deal for a full project development.”

Indiana Jones and the Fate of Atlantis Special Edition is a remake of legendary game Indiana Jones and the Fate of Atlantis (1992) made by Lucasfilm games.
Special Edition features high definition digital artwork, smooth, realistic animation, high quality music, sound effects and voice overs.

This game is in beta and it will not be released publicly until approved by Disney / Lucasfilm!

Indiana Jones and the Fate of Atlantis is a point-and-click adventure game by Lucasfilm games, originally released in 1992.
Disney. All rights reserved.

name: Immortal Sins
description: Step into the shoes of Maria, a noble girl on a distant island who was exiled for the murder of an important person, which she never committed. Now away from her mother and her little sister, she and Elena, a trainee Dragon slayer, will travel across cities and kingdoms to uncover the truth and seek redemption. However, what she finds may be the key to change the entire world…

name: Timo-T
description: 3D action-skill-platformer single/multiplayer game that follows a storyline where U can pick one of 3 characters and have to make your way through a constantly moving maze. Basically you have to collect a certain amount of keys/level to get to the next one and so on. The levels get harder as you progress in the game. The multiplayer part will have pvp arenas of max players of 4v4 and a CO-op version with more difficult levels.

name: Andromeda: There is No God Up Here
description:
"Andromeda is an exploration game, full Metroidvania style with 8-bit aesthetics and inspired by the great classics of the genre. Balancing story with play-ability and an open galaxy universe, we present a hardcore experience that you can only overcome by combining the DNA of your enemies in the DNA-GUN.

Do you dare to uncover the dark secret of Andromeda?"

name: Pixel Princess Blitz
description:
'PIXEL PRINCESS BLITZ' is a fantasy-themed roguelike action RPG.
It is inspired by awesome games such as 'D&D: Shadow over Mystara', 'FTL: Faster Than Light', and 'The Legend of Zelda'.
Featuring a combination of hack 'n' slash, dungeon crawling and a TRPG-spiced dynamic story, this game is intended to be a real treat for every gamer who loves roguelikes or traditional RPGs, and isn't afraid of challenges.

name: Parachronism: Order of Chaos
description: Parachronism: Order of Chaos is a 3D Action RPG with social simulation system as one of its elements. This game is created by a new indie game developers around the world.

name: Cuttle Scuttle
description:
Cuttle Scuttle is a retro co-op arcade game with a nod to several classics of the 1980s, including Bubble Bobble and Ms Pacman. 

It's breeding season at Point Lowly, and three female cuttlefish heroins, Lola, Lulu and Mimi, must navigate a hazardous series of rocky reefs, find cuttlefish mates and lay enough eggs to ensure their species' survival.

Brimming with tasty crustaceans, troublesome urchins, hungry dolphins and meddling humans, Cuttle Scuttle offers maze after maze of increasingly frantic action and plenty of surprises!

name: Lone Light
description: Lone Light is an atmospheric puzzle game about a source of light, alone in the universe trying to find its identity. Players have the control of the source of light, however, the source is not distinguishable from its surrounding. To figure out the position of the source and where it is going, players have to use the shadows created by the obstacles in the level to reach the destination, black holes, to enter the next level. Paying attention to the shadows is the most important aspect of the gameplay.

name: Runic - Legacy of Sin
description:
"Runic is an action-packed metroidvania currently being developed for PC. The game aims to bring a fresh new feel to the classic genre with the adaptation of RPG elements and a unique combo-centric combat system." 
 
"The Runic combat system is designed to be dynamic and interactive. 
 
Sometimes it's not enough to just run in swinging. Certain enemies are best defeated using more unorthodox methods. 
 
Some enemies can be supressed with a combo barrage. A sound mastery of the combo system is crucial if you really want to dish out the pain. 
 
Combos are also just plain old fun..."

name: Romance of the Three Kingdom Touch
World Championship Poker 2: Featuring Howard Lederer
Pole Position: Remix
description: An updated version of Pole Position for the click wheel iPod and iOS.

name: NFL 2010
description: A fully licensed NFL game for the iPhone.

name: Bangai-O HD
description: Bangai-O HD: Missile Fury is an innovative and insanely addicting, omni-directional arcade shooter combined with puzzle elements that feature a screen-filling, sensory overload of thousands of missiles! Loaded with more than 100 levels, players will conquer challenging obstacles, collect power-ups, and annihilate swarms of enemies and missiles to clear a level! Key game highlights include: a Level Editor Tool, which allows players to design and share their own levels with friends; a unique design style evident in the insane gameplay, from the types of enemies to the award system of collecting delectable fruit; and a combo system that lets players build up devastating counter attacks of up to 1,000 missiles for an explosive advantage!an explosive advantage!

name: The Network
description: The Network takes classic arena top-down shooting and adds a twist, you never fire a bullet. Collect packets and direct them into nodes while the AI is on your tail. Level up and grab more packets as you bring the fight to the AI.

name: Sneezies HD
description:
Grab a cup of tea, relax on your favorite beanbag, and enjoy the soothing, melodic gameplay and fantastic HD graphics in remastered version of the iPhone’s most addictive, casual viral game, Sneezies - an overload of cuteness!
Sneezies HD is now a universal app, including iPhone, iPod, iPad, & Apple TV support.
Drifting around the touchscreen are a host Sneezies with a tickle in their nose, ready to cause a chain reaction as their fellow balls of floating fluff sneeze, taking viral gameplay to a very literal new height.
Touch the screen to drop a burst of sneezing powder into the field of floating Sneezies and watch as they sneeze themselves out of their bubbles in a marvelous chain reaction. Try to rescue as many Sneezies as you can in one go by setting off the chain reaction at just the right place, and at just the right moment.
Play through 45 relaxing levels of Sneezies in the Classic Mode, or unleash your skills in the 15 Challenge Mode levels and post your high scores online to see how you stack up against other Sneezies players around the world.

name: Sound Shapes: Car Mini-Album & Creator Pack
Tiger Woods PGA Tour 14: Masters Historic Edition
Light in the Dark
description: Light in the Dark is a physics puzzle game for mobile devices from Dreamgate Studios.

name: Mind the Trap
description:
Venture as mice of chivalry descending into an ever-shifting dungeon filled with golden cheddar. Lethal traps and puzzles—and the greed of your friends—threaten your valiant pursuit for riches and glory. 

How will you and your friends cooperate? When will you betray them? In the end, only the most daring mouse knight can escape alive.

name: Challenge Me: Math Workout
description: A brain training game for the Nintendo DS.

name: Tablemen
description:
Tablemen is a VR RTS game, set in a steampunk setting. By using strategy and cunning, you conquer precious resources used to get more troops into the battlefield. 
 
But you are not alone. Face the AI in battle, or challenge a friend to see who really is the greatest commander.

name: Skytorn
description: Skytorn is a procedurally generated action adventure game, set in the ruins of a fallen world. Centuries after a mysterious cataclysm tore the world apart, humans have taken to the skies - ferrying their kin in airships, searching the remains for artifacts and survivors. Explorer Névoa ventures out across uncharted islands, left floating in the sky. Alone and armed only with a shovel, she is determined to carve her own path.

name: Kwari
description: A free-to-play online multiplayer first-person shooter.

name: Lineage II: The Chaotic Throne - The 1st Throne: The Kamael
description: Lineage II is a MMORPG by Korean developer NCsoft.

name: Circus Empire
description: A game where players can create and maintain their own circus.

name: Requiem: Bloodymare
description: The strangely named Requiem: Bloodymare is a Free-To-Play darkly themed massively multiplayer online role-playing game created by GRAVITY.

name: Dreamlords: The Reawakening
description: A freemium MMORTS game with RPG elements.

name: Ageod's American Civil War: The Blue and the Gray
Venice Deluxe
description: A puzzle shooter game that features a player controlled gondola that shoots various shapes at holes of the same shapes in effort to stop buildings from sinking into the waterways of Venice,Italy

name: Touch Darts
description: Touch Darts is a darts game developed by Full Fat Productions and SEGA Europe, and published by Agetec. It features a mix of individual dart competitions, mini-games and multiplayer modes.

name: Detective Conan: Tsuioku no Gensou
description: The fifth and final overall Detective Conan game developed by Bandai for the PlayStation. There was also a Trial version of the game released under the name Detective Conan: Trick Trick Vol 0.

name: Dark Age of Camelot: Labyrinth of the Minotaur
The Early Years of Flight
description: A biblical game where the player learns the story of Jesus' early years.

name: Air Rivals
description: Free MMO flight game. Formerly known as Flysis and Space Cowboy.

name: Out of the Park Baseball 9
description: Out of the Park Baseball 9 is the latest entry in a long-running PC baseball simulation. It is the first version since Out of the Park 6 developed solely by Out of the Park Developments.

name: Exidium Corp
description:
The Last Frontier is a sandbox MMO with a seamless and persistent world accessible at any time, from anywhere and from any device.
Colonize new lands, build new cities, explore unspoiled nature, form alliances, command armies; drive futuristic and powerful vehicles in a hostile and immense open-world.

name: WWII Battle Tanks: T-34 vs. Tiger
Pirates: Duels on the High Seas
Combat Mission Shock Force: Marines
description: The first expansion module for Combat Mission Shock Force featuring the US Marine Corps . The expansion includes a wide range of additional equipment for both the US and the Syrian forces, a new campaign, and numerous scenario battles.

name: X-COM Collection
description: 2016's entry in the advent-esque minigame collection series.

name: Captain Successor
description: The sequel to Captain Forever, Successor promises a variety of new ship parts, like torpedoes, homing missiles, ramming spikes, and auto-repair systems.

name: Tiger Woods PGA Tour Online
description: Tiger Woods PGA Tour Online is a browser based golf game, the first of it's kind for the popular Tiger Woods franchise.

name: The Kore Gang: Outvasion From Inner Space
Elminage II DS Remix: Sousei no Megami to Unmei no Daichi
Elminage DS Remix: Yami no Miko to Kamigami no Yubiwa
Twist Pilot
description: Action-puzzle game where the player has to guide a rotating stick creature through a maze while avoiding obstacles.

name: Timefight Zone
description: Timefight Zone is a Co-Op FPS that is best described as a mix of Left 4 Dead, Timesplitters, and Serious Sam. It's still very early in development, and you can see exactly how early by checking out our development videos!

name: NBA Rush
description: Endless runner in which NBA players battle an alien invasion.

name: The Drowning
description: First person shooter set in a post-apocalyptic world.

name: Monsters Invade: Oz
description: A free-to-play, monster-capturing RPG featuring hand-drawn graphics set in the world of The Wizard of Oz.

name: A Light In Chorus
description:
"What if you had to rebuild Earth-using only the contents of the 1977 Voyager Record?" 
 
"A Light In Chorus" is a first person adventure game about experiencing the world through strange new eyes. Players explore a submerged future Earth via the contents of a crash-landed time capsule, loosely inspired by the Voyager Golden Records. 
 
Using a proprietary engine- allowing an art style entirely made up of particles- players will transform the mysterious remains of Earth into a vibrant, musical landscape, morphing, sucking and swishing the objects into new forms around them.

name: Painkiller: Hell & Damnation - The Clock Strikes Meat Night
Fibble
description: Play as the quirky hero Gubble in this family friendly action/puzzle game.

name: Birth of America II: Wars in America 1750-1815
Robert D. Anderson & the Legacy of Cthulhu
Kinect Sports: Season Two - Midnight Mountain
Auto Assault
description: Auto Assault was a sci-fi-themed MMORPG where players fought battles from behind the wheels of armed-and-armored cars. It was shut down on August 31, 2007.

name: Earthrise: A Guild Investigation
description: Earthrise, also known as Earthrise: A Guild Investigation, is an adventure game designed and programmed by Matt Gruson and published for MS-DOS in 1990 by Interstel. The player assumes the role of an astronaut sent to an asteroid base to investigate why it has ceased communication. It uses a combination of a text-based interface with EGA graphics.

name: Enemy Engaged 2
description: Enemy Engaged 2 is the 2007 sequel to Enemy Engaged: Comanche vs Hokum, and was published by G2 Games.

name: Dungeon Explorer: Warriors of the Ancient Arts
Mini Ninjas Adventures
description: Control Hiro using Kinect gestures and voice commands as he fights to save his master.

name: Avatar Superstar
description: Use your Microphone or Kinect to sing to your favorite songs, and see how you measure up to your favorite artists.

name: Champs: Battlegrounds
description: A free to play multiplayer squad strategy game for iOS and Android devices.

name: Lords & Peasants
description: Lords & Peasants is a medieval real-time strategy and city building game developed by Inverted Cat Games. It has both single and multiplayer modes with up to 16 Players. Start out as a lord of a small village and develop it into a prospering city. Manage your city and rule over the peasants. Forge alliances and intimidate your enemies. Recruit an army and conquer the lands to create your kingdom.

name: Legends of War
description: Legends of War revolutionizes console strategy gaming, mixing turn-based tactics with action elements in a visually stunning setting. Assume the role of one of the most charismatic generals of World War II, General George S. Patton, Commander of the U.S. Third Army. Lead your troops as they battle their way from the blood soaked beaches of Normandy to the war torn streets of Berlin. Carefully plan your moves and make the right decisions to dominate the battlefield and lead your men to victory.

name: Flint and Charlie
description: Take the role of Charlie, a troubled teenager who's getting some grown up life experience by working with his eccentric scientist uncle, Professor Flint. The two of you go away on a dubious scavengehunt to raid an abandoned deep space research station. Things do not go as planned and soon you find yourself in quite the pickle, of galactic proportions!

name: Spellsword
description: Spellsword is an arcade-style fantasy action RPG for iOS platforms. Borrowing from games such as Super Crate Box, players collect spell cards and try to survive as long as possible against waves of fantasy enemies.

name: Grim Facade 7: Monster In Disguise
description: ERS Game Studios proudly presents the next installment of the Grim Facade series! A recent string of murders has been terrifying locals. The authorities thought they caught the real Bloody Stanley, but some new murders have them stumped. Could it be a copycat killer, or is the masked murderer still out there? It's up to you to solve the case. Will you find the killer before it's too late, or will you be the next victim? Find out in this chilling hidden-object puzzle adventure!
